        </paragraph>
        <paragraph id="2">
            <sentence id="2.1">Make a change to the item you just added.</sentence>
            <sentence id="2.2">Choose the edit menu.</sentence>
            <sentence id="2.3">Actual: Undo is not available.</sentence>
            <sentence id="2.4">Ctrl-Z does not undo the action.</sentence>
        </paragraph>
        <paragraph id="3">
            <sentence id="3.1">Expected, in both cases: Undo is available.</sentence>
            <sentence id="3.2">Ctrl-Z undoes the action.</sentence>
        </paragraph>
    </description>
